Primo Uy - 07/22/24  3:51:16 PM: We check the Holzma saw machine, and it has an error saying, "low air pressure". We check the main compressor and find out its stop running. Turn on the back up compressor. I clear the error. the machine start working after a while the back compressor was turn on.
Note;
The Homag Edge 2020 was also return to run again after Me and Ramon check the glue temp to its set temp of 195 C, it was on 135 C when Ramon tries to run the edge 220 again after the compressor swap. We clear all the error before we are able to run the normally.
